flowchart LR
  A[ADMIN] --> S[Billing Servlets]
  B[BILLING_STAFF] --> S
  R[RECEPTIONIST] --> S
  P[PATIENT read-only] --> S
  S --> BS[BillService]
  S --> PS[PaymentService]
  BS --> BD[BillDao]
  BS --> ID[BillItemDao]
  PS -->|lock bill row| BD
  PS --> PD[PaymentDao]
  BD --> O[(Oracle XE)]
  ID --> O
  PD --> O
  BS -->|transaction| C[Header + item insertion]
  PS -->|transaction| T[Payment + financial summary]
  T --> X{Amount exceeds locked balance?}
  X -->|yes| Block[Block overpayment]
  X -->|no| State[Partial or paid status]
  A --> Refund[Whole-payment refund]
  Refund --> PS
  S --> Print[Invoice / receipt print]
